<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><u>INDEMNITY AGREEMENT</u></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">In consideration of PHOENIX INSURANCE COMPANY LIMITED becoming Surety on the Performance Bond applied for by <strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>M/S&nbsp;JAVKIER LIMITED </strong>dated Friday 18th of March 2022 in&nbsp; favour of <strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>THE CHIEF OF STAFF, OFFICE OF THE PRESIDENT </strong>as Obligee (hereinafter called &ldquo;the Employer&rdquo;) in the amount <strong>GH&cent;136,505.19 (ONE HUNDRED AND THIRTY-SIX THOUSAND FIVE HUNDRED AND FIVE GHANA CEDIS NINETEEN PESEWAS)</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>we do hereby covenant and agree to pay the&nbsp; premium agreed upon, and we do hereby bind yourself, our heirs, executors, administrators, successors and assigns to indemnify the said PHOENIX INSURANCE COMPANY LIMITED (Surety&nbsp; Company) against all loss, costs, damages, charges and expenses, whatever and howsoever resulting from any act, default or neglect, that the said PHOENIX INSURANCE COMPANY LIMITED (Surety Company) may sustain or incur by reason of its having executed the said Bond or any continuation thereof.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We <strong>M/S&nbsp;JAVKIER LIMITED </strong>undertake to pay PHOENIX INSURANCE COMPANY LIMITED on receipt of their first demand without cavil or argument, any sum within the limits of <strong>GH&cent;136,505.19 (ONE HUNDRED AND THIRTY-SIX THOUSAND FIVE HUNDRED AND FIVE GHANA CEDIS NINETEEN PESEWAS)</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>as aforesaid and without any need to prove to show the reason for the demand and we <strong>M/S&nbsp;JAVKIER LIMITED </strong>will immediately without delay deliver the required sum and without the necessity of a previous notice or of Judicial or administrative procedures.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We <strong>M/S&nbsp;JAVKIER LIMITED </strong>hereby further agree for ourselves, our heirs, executors, administrators and assigns, to accept vouchers or any other evidence of any sum paid by the said PHOENIX INSURANCE COMPANY LIMITED (Surety Company) in completing the said Contract, as conclusive evidence against us and our estates of the fact and extent of our liability, under the said obligation to <strong>THE CHIEF OF STAFF, OFFICE OF THE PRESIDENT</strong> (Obligee).</p>
<h4 style="text-align: justify;">It is further expressly agreed that the said PHOENIX INSURANCE COMPANY LIMITED (Surety Company) possess that right to redeem the bond at its discretion even if we <strong>M/S&nbsp;JAVKIER LIMITED</strong> dispute our liability towards <strong>&nbsp; </strong><strong>THE CHIEF OF STAFF, OFFICE OF THE PRESIDENT</strong> (Obligee). No right of action shall accrue on this Bond to or for the use of any person or corporation other than the Employer named herein or the heirs, executors, administrators, successors and assigns of the Employer.</h4>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;In testimony whereof, the Contractor has hereunto set his hand and affixed his seal.</p>
